description:
The Bible regularly commands us to feed the poor and consider the needs of others. 

For the past 60 years, Meals on Wheels has been fulfilling this command, faithfully feeding thousands every day. 

Currently, this program has been feeding over 180,000 individuals daily in the south Africa region. 

Find more Adventist news from around the world on adventist.news
